thread.title: BRIEF-China Galaxy Securities issues 2018 2nd tranche corporate bonds worth totaling 2.2 bln yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-China Galaxy Securities issues 2018 2nd tranche corporate bonds worth totaling 2.2 bln yuan

organizations.name: reuters) - china galaxy securities co ltd

text:
Feb 13 (Reuters) - China Galaxy Securities Co Ltd :
* Says it completed issuance of 2018 2nd tranche corporate bonds
* 2-year bonds worth 1.2 billion yuan with coupon rate of 5.6 percent and 3-year bonds worth 1 billion yuan with coupon rate of 5.7 percent
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/mqvLG7
